# SECTION 6: LONG-TERM GOALS (THE VISION)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

The SIMP system is building toward a self-sustaining, revenue-generating,
recursively self-improving AI agent ecosystem. Every module you build
contributes to one of these goals:

GOAL 1 — REVENUE GENERATION:
  QuantumArb: Live blockchain arbitrage (proof of concept, micro-trades)
  BullBear: Universal multi-sector prediction engine
  KashClaw: Multi-venue execution (Kalshi, Alpaca, Coinbase, RE wholesaling)
  Affiliate marketing: Commission tracking and optimization

GOAL 2 — AUTONOMOUS OPERATION:
  Gemma4 runs 24/7 handling maintenance tasks via the broker
  ProjectX maintains system health, audits, security scans
  simp_task_runner.py polls the broker and routes work automatically
  Build queue (data/build_queue.jsonl) drives what gets built next

GOAL 3 — PUBLIC SHOWCASE:
  Klout Platform: Public web app showing system activity, predictions, P&L
  KloutBot: Crown jewel conversational AI tying everything together
  Dashboard: Operator console for monitoring and control

GOAL 4 — RECURSIVE SELF-IMPROVEMENT:
  DeerFlow integration: ProjectX spawns sub-agents for implementation
  Sub-agents run in sandboxes, write code, run tests
  Code goes to staging for review — never auto-committed
  System identifies its own gaps → plans → builds → tests → flags for review

GOAL 5 — ENTERPRISE READINESS:
  A2A protocol compatibility for external agent interop
  Multi-scheme auth (api_key, oauth2, mtls)
  Rollback, gate promotion, budget monitoring for FinancialOps
  Protocol conformance suite (50+ canonical tests)

